        {
            "title": "財經｜快手(01024)去年經調整盈利升16.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜快手(01024)去年經調整盈利升16.5%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZU5IM3jZZj4Rghx06ugxUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜快手(01024)去年經調整盈利升16.5%</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">快手(01024)公布，截至去年12月底止年度股東應佔盈利186.17億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年增長21.4%，每股盈利4.35元，派末期息0.69港元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">期內，經調整利潤淨額206.47億元，增長16.54%。收入1427.76億元，按年升12.51%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">單計去年第四季，經調整利潤淨額54.63億元，升16.21%。收入395.68億元，按年升11.82%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2025年第四季度，快手應用的平均日活躍用戶達到4.08億，按年穩健增長。2025全年，快手應用平均日活躍用戶達到4.1億。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">業務展望方面，隨着AI技術的快速演進，公司會堅持深耕AI戰略，加大AI的投入，進一步鞏固快手作為領先的AI賦能內容平台的定位，秉持「科技為本，用戶為先」的理念，始終以用戶需求為基礎，深化AI融合，幫助商家和營銷客戶提升運營效率。</p></div>",
